Sys::Statgrab - Extension of Unix::Statgrab for greater portability.

DESCRIPTION

See "perldoc Sys::Statgrab" (or "perldoc Sys/Statgrab.pm") for details.


PREREQUISITES

Sys::Statgrab requires the following perl modules:

- Unix::Statgrab

Sys::Statgrab may require the following perl modules, depending on your platform:

- Win32::Process:Info


INSTALLING

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install


